<p>I want to show the emotional consequences of hazing.</p>
<p>The 1st and 2nd interviews show the beginning: a child that is surrounded by peers who see him as &quot;the other&quot; and adults that laugh at him while doing nothing. But there is a difference here, he isn't irreparably scarred by the tree. He cries and feels shame about what happened.</p>
